---
title: Down-Home Rockfish Sandwiches with Coleslaw, Remoulade & Paprika Potato Wedges
description: Cue the brass band and get ready to “laissez le bon temps rouler” because your taste buds are about to take a trip to the Bayou! We’re talking ultra-crunchy rockfish fillets piled into brioche buns along with tangy coleslaw, creamy remoulade, and a drizzle of hot sauce. There’s even a side of paprika-spiced potato wedges for good measure. Now if we could only perfect our Hurricane cocktail…
